                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">552.241-70</xref>, Availability of Funds for the Next Fiscal Year or Quarter, in lieu of the FAR clause at <xref href="https://www.acquisition.gov/far/part-52#FAR_52_232_19"
